HEADWORD: Inhabitable
<hw>In*hab"it*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inhabitabilis</ets>. See <er>Inhabit</er>.]</ety> <def>Capable of
being inhabited; habitable.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Systems of <qex>inhabitable</qex> planets.</q>
