<p><ent>Inhabitable</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Inhabitable
<hw>In*hab"it*a*ble</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>inhabitabilis</ets>: cf. F. <ets>inhabitable</ets>. See
<er>In-</er> not, and <er>Habitable</er>.]</ety> <def>Not habitable; not
suitable to be inhabited.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The frozen ridges of the Alps⟦br⟧
Or other ground <qex>inhabitable</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj></p>

